 match or generate a currency symbol.  \n  \n- **value** to match or generate a monetary value.  \n  \n## Requirements  \n **Header:** \\<locale>  \n  \n **Namespace:** std  \n  \n## See Also  \n [Thread Safety in the C++ Standard Library](../standard-library/thread-safety-in-the-cpp-standard-library.md)\n\n\n\n"}